data.description: Come check out this MOVE IN READY home in Westerville/New Albany area with Columbus taxes! This home features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms with a HUGE basement, waiting to be finished with a bathroom rough in. *NEW HVAC 2022* The kitchen was redone with stunning backsplash, quartz countertops, extra deep sink, large island with a barstool seating area and the massive walk in pantry of your dreams. A custom patio was added to the backyard to complete the area. Updated flooring is all throughout the home that is scratch and water resistant, as well as a 2nd floor laundry room with storage, large primary bedroom and large closets all throughout. The community is equipped with a fitness center, pool, tennis courts, playground and open green space. This home is IT and has it all!
